summary: The dungeon is located near Halted Stream Camp between the camp and Whiterun but closer to the camp.
descriptionHtml:
[size=5]Work In Progress.[/size]
[size=4]
I made a ton of changes but the files ended up getting deleted :( so that made me stop modding for a long time.  I will not abandon this mod not until it is complete may take a while though.
[/size]
When I had first started the mod I had zero experience and I ended up deleting a static object (NorBgRmStairsL01 or something like that) but I re-added 71 references but there were I think 74 references so just watch your step and please tell me if you find where the stairs should be.


My first mod.  Posts/messages are welcome as well as any criticism.

This Largish dungeon that isn't done is really only uploaded for my friends to be able to download but if you want to download it go ahead.  I will be re-uploading it when I add stuff to it/when I finish it.

The center on cell(COC) command for the dungeon is COC TombOfRasenth (outside) and COC TombOfRasenthinterior01 (inside)

The dungeon is located just a little south of Halted Stream Camp.[size=4]

Install instructions:
[/size]
Download with manager
or 
Download, extract, and place files/folders in Skyrim's data folder.

Thank you for checking out my first mod I hope you enjoy it.
